com.ebay.soap.eBLBaseComponents
Class BusinessSellerDetailsType

java.lang.Object
  com.ebay.soap.eBLBaseComponents.BusinessSellerDetailsType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class BusinessSellerDetailsType
extends Object
implements Serializable

Displays the seller's information (in a business card format) as part of the data returned if the seller's SellerBusinessCodeType is set to 'Commercial'. Note that this option is only available for sites that have Business Seller options enabled.
